    'The kreds experience multiplier works as followed: 2 ^ prestige layers unlocked (or 1, if none are unlocked) ^ multipliers bought with kreds. So at layer 3, with 1 upgrade bought it would be 2^3^1 = x8.': 'K币经验乘数的工作原理如下：2 ^声望等级已解锁（或1，如果没有一个未解锁）^K币购买的乘数。 因此，在第3层，购买了1个升级，它将是2 ^ 3 ^ 1 = x8。',
    'The kreds soft-prestige multiplier works as followed: 2 ^ multipliers bought with kreds. So with 2 upgrades bought it would be 2^2 = x4. This multiplier is added before exponential floor scaling is applied. Keep in mind that this multiplier is applied to points gained, not (directly) to stats gained, as they increase in price.': '使用K币软声望加成的工作原理如下：用K币购买的2 ^乘数。 因此，如果购买了2个升级，它将是2 ^ 2 = x4。 在应用指数底限缩放之前，将添加此乘数。 请记住，此乘数适用于获得的积分，而不是（直接）适用于随着价格上涨而获得的属性。',
    '*****Adds the same amount of prestige points as this layer has to the layer below on floor change, including points spend on stats upgrades. This amount increases exponentially by the floor number reached. AutoBuyers also trigger if set to do so, without triggering an actual prestige.': '*****向该楼层更改的下一层添加与该层相同数量的声望积分，包括花费在属性升级上的积分。 此数量按所达到的楼层数呈指数增加。 如果设置为“自动购买”，也会触发自动购买者，而不会触发实际声望。',
    '****Resets lower layers to the same amount of prestige points as this layer has, including points spend on stats upgrades, instead of zero prestige points. AutoBuyers also trigger if set to do so.': '****将较低层重置为与该层相同的声望点数量，包括用于属性升级的点数，而不是零声望点。 如果设置为自动购买，也会触发自动购买。',
