    'The respawn improvement only works for respawns after dead, it won\'t trigger when prestiging or reskilling. Read as current floor minus amount. It is relative to your current floor.': '楼层增益功能仅适用于死后的重生，在声望重生和更改属性后不会触发。 具体效果为死后重生在当前楼层-增益数量的楼层',
    'When you have six or more heroes, you don\'t actually gain another hero, but your other heroes instead increase their stats to a similar degree.': '当您有六个或更多英雄时，您实际上并没有获得另一个英雄，但是您的其他英雄会将其属性提高到相似的程度。',
    'Resets lower layers to the same amount of prestige points as this layer has, including points spent on stats upgrades, instead of zero prestige points. AutoBuyers also trigger if set to do so. Disclaimer: If you prestige with enough points on this layer, the lower layer may gain enough to instantly allow you to prestige this layer again. Some of you were nice enough to report this as a bug, but it\'s not a bug. It won\'t hold up against normal progression (at least not for long': '将较低的图层重置为与该图层相同的声望值，包括属性升级所花费的点数，而不是零声望值。 如果设置为自动购买，也会触发自动购买。 免责声明：如果您在该层上有足够的声望，下层可能会获得足够的收益，可以立即让您再次声望此层。 你们当中有些人很好，可以将其报告为错误，但这不是错误。 它不会阻止正常进展（至少不会持续很长时间）',
