    //K币升级类
    'The kreds experience multiplier works as followed: 2 ^ prestige layers unlocked (or 1, if none are unlocked) ^ (ascension layers unlocked x10) ^ multipliers bought with kreds. So at prestige layer 20, ascension layer 1, with 1 upgrade bought it would be 2^20^10^1 = x1.61e60.': 'kreds经验乘数的工作原理如下：2 ^解锁声望层（或1，如果没有一个被解锁）^（转生层未锁定x10）^用kred购买的乘数。 因此，在声望层20，转生层1中，购买了1个升级，它将是2 ^ 20 ^ 10 ^ 1 = x1.61e60。',
    'The kreds gold gain and soft-prestige multiplier works as followed: 2 ^ multipliers bought with kreds. So with 2 upgrades bought it would be 2^2 = x4. This multiplier is added before exponential floor scaling is applied. Keep in mind that this multiplier is applied to points gained, not (directly) to stats gained, as they increase in price.': 'K币的金增益和软声望乘数的工作原理如下：用K币购买2 ^乘数。 因此，如果购买了2个升级，它将是2 ^ 2 = x4。 在应用指数底限缩放之前，将添加此乘数。 请记住，此乘数适用于获得的积分，而不是直接适用于随着价格增加而获得的属性信息。',
    '2 ^ multipliers bought with kreds. So with 2 upgrades bought it would be 2^2 = x4.': '2^K币购买乘数，所以购买1次升级后获得2^2=4倍金币加成',
    '2 ^ prestige layers unlocked (or 1, if none are unlocked) ^ kreds upgrades. So at layer 3, with 1 kreds upgrade bought it would be 2^3^1 = x8.': '2^已解锁声望层数（如果未解锁则为1）^K币购买升级，所以当你解锁声望第三层，并且购买1次K币升级后将会获得2^3^1=8倍经验加成',
    'Unit size': '单位大小',
    'Yes. There are more layers to prestige. They consume all of your previous prestige points, as well as points spend on stats upgrades. This will set you back a bit, but allow you to reach even higher numbers when you proceed.  And once get to around prestige layer 20, you\'ll unlock ascension which offer a whole new mechanic to further push your limits': '是。 声望还有更多层次。 他们消耗了您之前所有的声望点，以及花费在属性升级上的点。 这会让您有点退缩，但是在继续操作时，您甚至可以达到更高的数字。 到达声望第20层后，您将解锁转生，这提供了一种全新的机制来进一步突破极限',
    'You are currently not logged in to Kongregate. To use the kreds shop, please log in. If you have already bought anything, the numbers below will correct themselves after you\'ve logged in.': '您当前尚未登录Kongregate。 要使用K币商店，请登录。如果您已经购买了任何东西，那么登录后，以下数字将自动更正。',
    'The first hour gives 100% progress, after that you get hours offline ^0.95, up to a maximum of 24 hours of offline progress, obtained after roughly 28 hours of being offline. This means offline progress is 83-100% as effective as online progress. If you have played less than 200 hours (including offline progress), this cap is lowered accordingly, to not overwhelm new players with too much offline progress. The first five hours of the offline progress cap are obtained in about 15 hours of playtime, the first hour of offline progress is obtained in an hour.': '第一个小时提供100％的进度，此后，您可以使离线时间达到^ 0.95，最多可以达到24个小时的离线进度，这大约是在离线28个小时后获得的。 这意味着离线进度是在线进度的83-100％。 如果您玩的时间少于200小时（包括离线进度），则此上限会相应降低，以免离线进度过多的新玩家不知所措。 离线进度上限的前五个小时是在15个小时的播放时间中获得的，离线进度的前一个小时是在一小时内获得的。',
